lead_paragraph: Midfielder Bastian Schweinsteiger won his 121st cap in his last match for Germany as they beat Finland 2-0 in an international friendly in Moenchengladbach on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Schweinsteiger Bows Out as Germany Beat Finland
